Classifier: Programming Language :: Python
Classifier: License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License v3 (GPLv3)
Classifier: Topic :: Scientific/Engineering :: Astronomy
Requires: astropy
Requires: numpy
Requires: matplotlib
Provides: mocpy
